If you want to make any comments or feature requests, please post in 
the Sourceforge forums at the Sourceforge project page:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/mesh2hmap.

The direct link to the forum is:
	http://sourceforge.net/forum/forum.php?forum_id=548393

If you find a bug go to the sourceforge page and submit a bug report 
in the 'Bug Tracking System'. Click on the 'Submit New' link in the 
upper left, then post the command you used, the output you got, and a 
link to the VRML file you were trying to use.

The direct link to the Bug Tracker is:
	http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=161953&atid=821908
